{"word":"κάτοπτρον","slug":"κάτοπτρον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κάτοπτρον</b></el> <el>(κάτ-οπτρον, ου, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ὄψομαι</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> of <a href='S:ὁράω'><el>ὁράω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a mirror</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>speculum</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>a mere reflexion</i> (not a reality), <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}